            <title><![CDATA[【[吃惊]#岁数大了身体出现这些味道或是生病了#】随着年龄增大，人体会出现“老人味”，这种味道多与身体疾病、个人卫生等问题相关。最常见的几种“老人味”：①...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B2%81%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%86%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%91%B3%E9%81%93%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9F%E7%97%85%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B2%81%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%86%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%91%B3%E9%81%93%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9F%E7%97%85%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#岁数大了身体出现这些味道或是生病了#</span></a>】随着年龄增大，人体会出现“老人味”，这种味道多与身体疾病、个人卫生等问题相关。最常见的几种“老人味”：①烂苹果味，常见于重度糖尿病患者；②氨臭味，常见于肾功能不全的病人；③酸臭味，常见于有消化道疾病的患者；④腐败的味道，常见于老年女性有妇科疾病的患者。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些方法可以缓解老人味#</span></a>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6WE6BsJ" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
